reviewtext: What a deal! I received 3 cartridges of labeling tape with free shipping for LESS than the retail cost of 1 at a B&M store! Free shipping takes a bit longer but that was a choice I was willing to accept.  Product was exactly as what I would expect to receive at a retail store.  I am delighted to get more for my dollar without having to sacrifice on quality. Thanks! Will do business again...and again....and again!!
